# Use this document for getting the stack for building your App

A concise, modern checklist for launching a SaaS MVP that can make money. Each component includes a one-liner on its purpose and the top 1â€“3 tool choices.

## Core Tech Stack

### Frontend Framework
- [ ] **Next.js**: React-based framework for fast, SEO-friendly web apps with SSR/SSG.

### Frontend Language
- [ ] **TypeScript**: Typed superset of JavaScript for safer, more maintainable code.

### Backend Framework
- [ ] **Node.js + Express**: Minimal, fast backend for APIs and business logic.
- [ ] **NestJS**: TypeScript-first, structured backend framework for scalable APIs.

### Database
- [ ] **PostgreSQL**: Reliable, scalable relational database for structured data.
- [ ] **Supabase**: Managed Postgres with real-time APIs, auth, and storage for rapid MVPs.

### ORM / Database Toolkit
- [ ] **Prisma**: Type-safe ORM for modeling, migrations, and querying your database.

### Styling & UI
- [ ] **Tailwind CSS**: Utility-first CSS for rapid, responsive design.
- [ ] **shadcn/ui**: Accessible, customizable React component library built on Tailwind.

### Authentication
- [ ] **Clerk**: Plug-and-play user authentication, management, and UI components.
- [ ] **NextAuth.js**: Flexible authentication for Next.js apps (if not using Clerk).

### Payments
- [ ] **Stripe**: Payment processing and subscription billing for SaaS products.

### Email Delivery
- [ ] **Resend**: Simple, developer-friendly transactional email API.

### Hosting / Deployment
- [ ] **Vercel**: Zero-config hosting for Next.js and serverless backends.
### Database Hosting
- [ ] **Supabase**: Managed Postgres with instant APIs and auth.

### Monitoring & Logging
- [ ] **Sentry**: Real-time error tracking and performance monitoring.
- [ ] **LogRocket**: Session replay and frontend monitoring for web apps.
- [ ] **Prometheus**: Metrics collection and monitoring for infrastructure and applications.
- [ ] **Grafana**: Visualization and alerting for metrics and logs.

### Analytics
- [ ] **PostHog**: Product analytics and user behavior tracking (self-hosted or cloud).

### API Documentation
- [ ] **OpenAPI**: Standard for documenting and testing REST APIs.

### API Gateway (optional for MVP)
- [ ] **Kong**: Open-source API gateway for managing and securing APIs.

### Containerization
- [ ] **Docker**: Containerize and deploy your app consistently across environments.

### Caching
- [ ] **Redis**: In-memory data store for caching and real-time features.

### Live Chat / Support (optional)
- [ ] **Crisp**: Live chat widget for customer support and onboarding.

### Prototyping / Design
- [ ] **Figma**: Collaborative design and prototyping tool for UI/UX.

### CI/CD
- [ ] **GitHub Actions**: Automate testing and deployment workflows.

### Version Control
- [ ] **GitHub**: Source code hosting and collaboration platform.

### Environment Management
- [ ] **Dotenv**: Manage environment variables for local development.

### Testing Frameworks
- [ ] **Jest**: Standard testing framework for JavaScript/TypeScript unit and integration tests.
- [ ] **Playwright**: Modern end-to-end testing for web applications.

### Task Scheduling / Background Jobs
- [ ] **BullMQ**: Redis-based queue for handling background jobs in Node.js.

### Secrets Management
- [ ] **Doppler**: Unified secrets and configuration management for teams.

### Backup & Disaster Recovery
- [ ] **Automated Backups**: Verify and configure backup settings in your DB provider.
- [ ] **Recovery Plan**: Document restore procedures and test them periodically.

### Legal & Compliance
- [ ] **Privacy Policy**: Required for data collection and GDPR compliance.
- [ ] **Terms of Service**: Define service terms and limitations.
- [ ] **Cookie Policy**: Required for EU users if using cookies/tracking.

### Multi-Tenancy Support
- [ ] **Database Design**: Implement row-level security and tenant isolation.
- [ ] **Auth Integration**: Configure Clerk/NextAuth.js for organization/team support.

